<p><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200830/4f3ed18e135448068ef5306d1888c587.png" width="100%" height="auto" /></p>
<p><strong><span>我叫文</span></strong></p>
<p><span>“</span><strong><span>李杜文章在，光焰万丈长</span></strong><span>”的</span><strong><span>文</span></strong><span>文采风流，首推李杜</span><span>学习先贤是我的追求</span></p>
<p><strong><span>我叫龙</span></strong></p>
<p><span>“</span><strong><span>鸿雁长飞光不度</span></strong><span>，</span><strong><span>鱼龙潜跃水成文</span></strong><span>”的</span><strong><span>龙</span></strong><span>鱼龙跳跃，激荡水纹</span><span>飞龙在天是我的人生之志</span></p>
<p><strong><span>我叫晨</span></strong></p>
<p><span>“</span><strong><span>盛年不重来，一日难再晨</span></strong><span>”的</span><strong><span>晨</span></strong><span>时光易逝，我自惜之</span><span>珍惜光阴是我的信条</span></p>
<p><strong><span>我叫梦</span></strong></p>
<p><span>“</span><strong><span>昨夜闲潭梦落花</span></strong><span>”的</span><strong><span>梦</span></strong><span>柔情似水，佳期如梦</span><span>温柔婉约是我的风格</span></p>
<p><strong><span>我叫飞</span></strong></p>
<p><span>“</span><strong><span>俱怀逸兴壮思飞，</span></strong><strong><span>欲上青天览明月</span></strong><span>”的</span><strong><span>飞</span></strong><span>蓄势待发，一飞冲天</span><span>直上云霄是我的目标</span></p>
<p><strong><span>我叫雨</span></strong></p>
<p><span>“</span><strong><span>梨花一枝春带雨</span></strong><span>”的</span><strong><span>雨</span></strong><span>花艳欲滴，春风习习</span><span>梨花带雨是我的愁绪</span></p>
<p><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200830/43ceb4222f7a4119b63e55bcda598f62.jpeg" width="100%" height="auto" /></p>
<p><strong><span>我叫欣</span></strong></p>
